1. Modify the variable WSOCKS_PREFIX in the Makefile, if you want to install
   it to an other directory instead of the default one "/usr/local".
2. type the command
      make && make install
   in the current directoy.
3. edit the config file libwsocks.acl in the directory WSOCKS_PREFIX/etc
4. use the command
      wsocks command ...
   to make this command use the special proxy transparently.
